subject: Wimbledon Tennis Tournament
Tennis
lead_paragraph: The veterans stopped the rising stars as Novak Djokovic defeated Grigor Dimitrov, 6-4, 3-6, 7-6 (2), 7-6 (7), and Roger Federer beat Milos Raonic, 6-4, 6-4, 6-4.
